# Documentation Contributor Guide

## Overview

Documentation site built with **Mintlify**. Lives in `docs/` directory.

## Directory Structure

```
docs/
├── mint.json                 # Mintlify config (nav, tabs, API settings)
├── getting-started/          # Intro & quickstart
├── product/                  # Product documentation
├── developer/                # Developer guides
├── api-reference/
│   ├── overview.mdx          # API overview with test endpoint
│   ├── endpoints/            # Individual API endpoint pages
│   └── openapi.json          # OpenAPI spec
├── guides/                   # How-to guides
├── starters/                 # Starter template docs
├── use-cases/                # Use case examples
└── public/                   # Static assets (logos, favicon)
```

## MDX Guidelines

### Formatting Rules

- **Line length**: Keep under ~100 characters
- **No JSX artifacts**: Never use `{" "}` - causes rendering issues
- **Inline exports only**: Mintlify doesn't support importing from `.ts` files

```mdx
<!-- ✅ Correct: inline export -->

export const items = [{ title: "Item 1" }];

<!-- ❌ Wrong: external import -->

import { items } from "./data.ts";

;
```

### Frontmatter

```yaml
---
title: "Page Title" # Main heading
sidebarTitle: "Sidebar Name" # Optional: different name in sidebar
description: "Brief description"
---
```

### Mintlify Components

````mdx
<Note>Informational callout</Note>
<Tip>Helpful suggestion</Tip>
<Warning>Important caution</Warning>

